---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Getting Started Guide - AIVancePro"
  description="Start using AIVancePro in 5 minutes. Step-by-step guide to set up your profile and launch your first workout."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/en/getting-started/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/guide-demarrage/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/getting-started/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/erste-schritte/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .guide-header { padding: 6rem 2rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, var(--bg) 100%); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
      .guide-header .section-label { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
      .guide-header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
      .guide-header p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }

      .steps { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem; position: relative; }
      .steps::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 2rem; top: 3rem; bottom: 2rem; width: 2px; background: var(--border); margin-left: 19px; }
      .step { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; position: relative; }
      .step-number { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--blue); color: #fff; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; z-index: 1; }
      .step-content h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
      .step-content p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }
      .step-content a { color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; }
      .step-content a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

      .bonus-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem 2rem; }
      .bonus-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.75rem; }
      .bonus-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; }
      .bonus-card h3 svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--blue); }
      .bonus-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }

      .guide-cta { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 2rem 5rem; text-align: center; }
      .guide-cta h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
      .guide-cta p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .guide-header { padding: 4.5rem 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
        .guide-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        .steps::before { left: 1.5rem; margin-left: 19px; }
        .steps { padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="guide-header">
    <div class="section-label">Getting started</div>
    <h1>Getting Started Guide</h1>
    <p>Start using AIVancePro in 5 minutes.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Download the app</h3>
        <p>AIVancePro is available for free on <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" target="_blank" rel="noopener">iOS (App Store)</a> and <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aivancepro.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Android (Google Play)</a>. Installation takes less than a minute.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Create your account</h3>
        <p>Sign up with your email, Google or Apple. It takes 30 seconds. You automatically get 7 days of Pro features for free.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Set up your profile</h3>
        <p>Enter your level (beginner, intermediate, advanced), your goals (muscle gain, strength, weight loss) and your available equipment. The AI adapts to you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Start your first session</h3>
        <p>Ask the AI coach to generate a session tailored to you, or browse the 240+ exercises to create your own. Each exercise includes detailed instructions and illustrations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">5</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Track your progress</h3>
        <p>After each session, your performance is automatically recorded. Check your stats, charts and personal records in the Progress tab.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bonus-section">
    <div class="bonus-card">
      <h3>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        The AI Coach
      </h3>
      <p>Your AI coach is available 24/7. Ask it anything about training, nutrition or recovery. With the Pro plan (first month at &euro;3.49), you get 250 messages per month and access to training plans up to 12 weeks.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="guide-cta">
    <h2>Ready to start?</h2>
    <p>Download AIVancePro and launch your first workout today.</p>
    <div class="store-badges" style="justify-content:center">
      <a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="store-badge-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.71 19.5c-.83 1.24-1.71 2.45-3.05 2.47-1.34.03-1.77-.79-3.29-.79-1.53 0-2 .77-3.27.82-1.31.05-2.3-1.32-3.14-2.53C4.25 17 2.94 12.45 4.7 9.39c.87-1.52 2.43-2.48 4.12-2.51 1.28-.02 2.5.87 3.29.87.78 0 2.26-1.07 3.8-.91.65.03 2.47.26 3.64 1.98-.09.06-2.17 1.28-2.15 3.81.03 3.02 2.65 4.03 2.68 4.04-.03.07-.42 1.44-1.38 2.83M13 3.5c.73-.83 1.94-1.46 2.94-1.5.13 1.17-.34 2.35-1.04 3.19-.69.85-1.83 1.51-2.95 1.42-.15-1.15.41-2.35 1.05-3.11z"/></svg>
        <span class="store-badge-text"><span class="small">Available on</span><span class="big">App Store</span></span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.aivancepro.app" class="store-badge-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M3.18 23.67c-.38-.39-.58-.94-.58-1.6V1.93c0-.66.2-1.21.58-1.6l.08-.08L14.74 11.7v.22L3.26 23.38l-.08-.08z"/><path d="M18.56 15.58l-3.82-3.84v-.22l3.82-3.84.08.05 4.53 2.57c1.29.73 1.29 1.93 0 2.67l-4.53 2.57-.08.04z" opacity=".8"/><path d="M18.65 15.53L14.74 11.6 3.18 23.2c.43.45 1.13.51 1.93.06l13.54-7.73" opacity=".6"/><path d="M18.65 7.68L5.11.95c-.8-.45-1.5-.39-1.93.06L14.74 12.6l3.91-3.92z" opacity=".6"/></svg>
        <span class="store-badge-text"><span class="small">Available on</span><span class="big">Google Play</span></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
